### Hadith 3:518

*Narrated Abu Huraira:*

The Ansar said to the Prophet "Distribute the date palm trees between us
and our emigrant brothers." He replied, "No." The Ansar said (to the
emigrants), "Look after the trees (water and watch them) and share the
fruits with us." The emigrants said, "We listen and obey."

